data.description: Welcome home to this stunning property nestled in the heart of Wheaton. Situated on over 1 acre of picturesque land, this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers unparalleled comfort and convenience. Large primary suite features a full bath with jetted tub, a walk in shower, dual vanity sink and multiple closets.  2 living areas will give you some room to stretch out.  Split bedroom plan.  Additional room available for a 4th bedroom if desired.  Storm shelter on the back porch.  Includes a versatile outbuilding with heat and electric, perfect for a second residence, workshop, or studio. Experience the latest in technology with a smart home system, complete with GoBec fiber optic for high-speed connectivity. House is networked with a state of the art wifi system. Property has 1.4 acres m/l of level yard.  A large portion of the yard is fenced.  Large deck is built for an above ground pool.  Also has a fire pit and basketball goal.
